title: Miranda (01 - 03 (of 06) (Comeuppance) (2003)
description:
Miranda (01 - 03 (of 06) (Comeuppance) (2003)



Spin-off comic from the Doctor Who novel series, following the adventures of the Doctor's adopted daughter, Miranda Dawkins. Written by Miranda's creator, novelist Lance Parkin, poor sales saw the comic cancelled after three issues, only halfway through its projected run. For copyright reasons, the Doctor himself does not appear in the series, nor is he directly named
